<h1>The RwxDevice Package</h1>
<p align="right">Recent release: <a href="@TAR_FILE@">@TAR_FILE@</a></p>
<p align="right">@DATE@</p>

This package provides an R graphics device that draws plots
on the screen using an wxWindow.
It is in its early stage, however, 
it will provide a platform-independent graphics device.
Additionally, it can be embedded into other widgets
an so allows embedding R graphics into more complex GUIs
ranging from scrolled devices, notebooks and more complex 
See <a href="../RwxWidgets">RwxWidgets</a>
for more information on creating GUIs in R using
wxWidgets.

